[src:chi-squared-tests/pearson-s-chi-squared-test] Let $\chi _{P}^{2}(\{k_{i}\},\{p_{i}\})$ be Pearson's cumulative test statistic for such a configuration, and let $\chi _{P}^{2}(\{p_{i}\})$ be the distribution of this statistic.
